Entity Space

Action perform_space_creation
  EventInput
    name          required
    icon          optional
    color         optional
    description   optional
  BusinessRules
    - User must not already have a space with the same name
  Steps
    - Create Space record with status = Active
  SideEffects
    - None
  ActionResult
    space_id      UUID

Action perform_space_update
  EventInput
    space_id      required
    name          optional
    icon          optional
    color         optional
    description   optional
  BusinessRules
    - At least one field must be provided for update
  Steps
    - Update provided fields on Space record
  SideEffects
    - None
  ActionResult
    space_id      UUID
    updated_fields  string[]

Action perform_space_archive
  EventInput
    space_id      required
  BusinessRules
    - None
  Steps
    - Update Space status to Archived
    - Cascade: update all Activities in space to status = Archived
    - Cascade: update all Tasks in space to status = Archived
    - Cascade: update all Notes in space to status = Archived
    - Cascade: update all CalendarEntries in space to archived = true
    - Cascade: update all Summaries in space to status = Closed
  SideEffects
    - None
  ActionResult
    space_id          UUID
    archived_counts   object    counts of each entity type archived

Action notify_already_archived
  EventInput
    space_id      required
  Steps
    - No state change
  ActionResult
    space_id      UUID
  Outcome
    NoAction      SPACE_ALREADY_ARCHIVED

Action reject_request
  Steps
    - No state change
  ActionResult
    None
  Outcome
    NoAction      REQUEST_REJECTED

Action perform_search
  EventInput
    space_id      required
    query         required
    entity_types  optional
  BusinessRules
    - query must be at least 2 characters
  Steps
    - Execute full-text search across requested entity types within space
    - Search targets: Task.title, Task.description, Note.title, Note.body,
      Activity.name, Activity.description, CalendarEntry.title,
      CalendarEntry.description, TaskComment.content
    - Return ranked results
  SideEffects
    - None
  ActionResult
    results       object[]    list of matches with entity_type, entity_id, title, excerpt, score
    total_count   integer
